title: IHF.Handball.Challenge.14.PS3-DUPLEX
description:
- D U P L E X -

P R O U D L Y P R E S E N T S :

IHF Handball Challenge 14

Date : 03/2014 Languages: English
Platform : PS3 Genre : Sports

Release Info:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~

The first handball simulation for consoles Handball fans will finally
be able to test themselves, gamepad in hand, thanks to the first
simulation offering 20 national teams and 80 teams from the most
prestigious leagues: The Ligue Nationale de Handball (France), the
Toyota Handball-Bundesliga (Germany), and the Liga Asobal (Spain).

You can also create your own players, make up a team, and participate
in national leagues and international tournaments, or compete against
up to 3 of your friends in a quick game.
